2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes an approach that combines modular architectures and end-to-end deep learning approaches, which falls under the domain of AI. 
3. cs.CV (Computer Vision): The paper mentions the use of perceptual input, which suggests the involvement of computer vision techniques. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper proposes a machine learning approach for training driving policies. 
5. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper discusses the use of classic driving systems and modular architectures, which falls under the domain of systems and control.
